<% provide(:title, 'Home') %>
<body style="background-color: #D3D3D3">
<div class="container-fluid" id="home-index">
	<div class="text-center index-block" id="beginning-block">
		<h1><strong>WELCOME!</strong></h1>
		<p>Search a movie at the search bar and make a selection from the autocomplete list</p>
		<p>OR</p>
		<p>Click the MOVIES tab</p>
	</div>
	<div class="lightgray-block">
		<div class="text-center index-block">
			<p>On the MOVIES tab, there will be a list of all the movies.</p>
			<p>You will have the ability to sort the movies (default is A-Z). There is also a feature that randomly selects a movie for you.</p>
		</div>
		<img src="/assets/movies_tab.png" class="img-center img-home" id="img_movies_tab">
		<div class="text-center index-block">
			<p>Both IMDb and RottenTomatoes ratings are displayed and a link to the page on the respective websites are provided.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="gray-block">
	<div class="text-center index-block">
		<p>The movie information page provides the following: the director, the release date, the runtime, an overview of the movie, the trailer for the movie, and lastly, the cast.</p>
	</div>
	<img src="/assets/movies_info.png" class="img-center img-home" id="img_movies_info">
	</div>
</div>
</body>
